sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin / User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VAReconciler as VA Reconciler
    participant CMReconciler as ConfigMap Reconciler
    participant Config as Config Object<br/>(in-memory)
    participant SatEngine as Saturation Engine<br/>(30s loop)
    participant SFZEngine as Scale-from-Zero Engine<br/>(100ms loop)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus / Thanos<br/>9090/TCP HTTPS
    participant EPP as EPP Pods<br/>HTTPS
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Actuator as Actuator<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DirectAct as DirectActuator
    participant HPAKEDA as HPA / KEDA

    Note over Admin,HPAKEDA: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create VariantAutoscaling CR
    K8sAPI-->>VAReconciler: Watch event (VA created)
    VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: Resolve scale target<br/>(Deployment/LWS)

    loop Every 30 seconds
        SatEngine->>Prometheus: PromQL: vllm:kv_cache_usage_perc,<br/>vllm:num_requests_waiting, token rates<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Prometheus-->>SatEngine: Per-replica metrics
        SatEngine->>SatEngine: Run analysis<br/>(V1/V2/Queueing Model)
        SatEngine->>Cache: Store scaling decision<br/>(desired replicas per VA)
        Cache-->>VAReconciler: Channel trigger
    end

    VAReconciler->>Cache: Read decision
    VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: Patch VA status<br/>(desired replicas, conditions)
    VAReconciler->>Actuator: Update Prometheus metrics<br/>(wva_desired_replicas, wva_desired_ratio)
    HPAKEDA->>Actuator: GET /metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Actuator-->>HPAKEDA: wva_desired_replicas=N
    HPAKEDA->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment<br/>(scale subresource)

    Note over Admin,HPAKEDA: Flow 2: Scale-from-Zero

    loop Every 100 milliseconds
        SFZEngine->>EPP: Scrape flow_control_queue_size<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (epp-metrics-token)
        EPP-->>SFZEngine: Queue size > 0
    end

    SFZEngine->>DirectAct: Scale up immediately
    DirectAct->>K8sAPI: PATCH scale subresource<br/>(replicas: 0 → 1)
    SFZEngine->>Cache: Store decision
    Cache-->>VAReconciler: Channel trigger
    VAReconciler->>K8sAPI: Patch VA status

    Note over Admin,HPAKEDA: Flow 3: ConfigMap Configuration

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>(saturation-scaling-config)
    K8sAPI-->>CMReconciler: Watch event
    CMReconciler->>Config: Update config object
    Config-->>SatEngine: Next loop reads<br/>updated parameters
